# Analytics API Specification

## Base URL
```
https://api.analytics.com/v1
```

## Authentication
All API requests require authentication via Bearer token:
```
Authorization: Bearer <your-api-token>
```

## Common Headers
```
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
```

## Data Models

### Student
```json
{
  "studentId": "string",
  "name": "string", 
}
```
### Question
```json
 {
  "studentId": "string",
  "courseId": "string";
  "year": "integer";
  "sem"; "integer";
  "examId": "string";  
  "questionId": "string";
  "questionType": "string";
  "topicId": "string";
  "answer": "string";
  "answerChangeCount": "integer";   // Number of answer changes
  "flagged": "boolean";
}
```
### Exam
```json
 {
  "studentId": "string",
  "courseId": "string";
  "year": "integer";
  "sem"; "integer";
  "examId": "string";
  "totalDuration": "float";         // In seconds
  "flaggedCount": "integer";
  "questions": Question[];
}
```

