## Endpoints

### 1. Get Student Exam Information

**GET** `/examInfo/{studentId}/{courseId}/{year}/{sem}/{examId}`

Retrieve specific basic information exam of a student.

#### Query Parameters
| Parameter | Type | Required | Description |
|-----------|------|----------|-------------|
| studentId | string | Yes | Filter by student ID |
| courseID | string | Yes | Filter by course ID |
| year | integer | Yes | Filter by year the course is taken |
| sem | integer | Yes | Filter by the semester the course is taken |
| examId | string | Yes | Filter by exam ID |

#### Example Request
```bash
curl -X GET "https://api.analytics.com/v1/examInfo/20719437/COMP1021/2024/1/midterm" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer your-token" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json"
```

#### Example Response
```json
{
  "data": [
    {
    "studentId": "20719437";
    "courseId": "COMP1021";
    "year": 2024;
    "sem"; 1;
    "examId": "midterm";
    "totalDuration": 3509.3;
    "flaggedCount": 3;
    "questions": [
        {
          "studentId": "20719437";
          "courseId": "COMP1021";
          "year": 2024;
          "sem"; 1;
          "examId": "exam1";
          "questionId": "1";
          "questionType": "essay";
          "topicId": "Heat";
          "answer": "The temperature is decreasing by 20%.";
          "answerChangeCount": 2;
          "flagged": true;
        },
        {
          "studentId": "20719437";
          "courseId": "COMP1021";
          "year": 2024;
          "sem"; 1;
          "examId": "exam1";
          "questionId": "2";
          "questionType": "essay";
          "topicId": "Wavelength";
          "answer": "The sound is traversing at 350 km/h.";
          "answerChangeCount": 0;
          "flagged": false;
        }
      ];
    }
  ],
  "success": true,
  "message": "Exam information retrieved successfully"
}
```

#### Response Codes
- `200` - Success
- `400` - Bad Request
- `401` - Unauthorized
- `404` - Student or exam not found
- `500` - Internal Server Error

