### 6. Update Analysis & Recommendations (TA Approval/Comment)

**POST** `/studentRecs/{studentId}/{courseId}/{year}/{sem}/{examId}/{questionId}`

Add or update human feedback/approval for the AI analysis and recommendation given for a specific student and question.

#### Query Parameters
| Parameter | Type | Required | Description |
|-----------|------|----------|-------------|
| studentId | string | Yes | Filter by student ID |
| examId | string | Yes | Filter by exam ID |
| courseID | string | Yes | Filter by course ID |
| year | integer | Yes | Filter by year the course is taken |
| sem | integer | Yes | Filter by the semester the course is taken |
| questionId | string | Yes | Filter by question ID |

#### Request Body
{
  "feedback": "Good initial attempt. Please additionally review topic notes on Heat transfer and revisit Q2 explanation in class slides.",
}

#### Example Request
```bash
curl -X POST "https://api.analytics.com/v1/studentRecs/20719437/COMP1021/2025/2/midterm/2" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer TA-token" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{ 
        "feedback": "Good initial attempt. Please additionally review topic notes on Heat transfer and revisit Q2 explanation in class slides.",
      }'
```

#### Example Response
```json
{
  "data": [
    {
      "studentId": "20719437",
      "courseId": "COMP1021",
      "year": 2025,
      "sem": 2,
      "examId": "midterm",
      "questionId": "2",
      "topicId": "Heat",
      "feedback": "Good initial attempt. Please additionally review topic notes on Heat transfer and revisit Q2 explanation in class slides.",
      "humanApproved": true,
      "feedbackApprover": "Hans B.",
      "approvedAt": "2025-11-08T19:31:00+08:00"
    }
  ],
  "success": true,
  "message": "Recommendation and feedback updated successfully."
}
```

#### Response Codes
- `201` - Created/Updated successfully
- `400` - Bad Request
- `401` - Unauthorized
- `404` - Student or exam or question not found
- `500` - Internal Server Error

